content:
Set Up Digital Lending for Financial Services Cloud.

Assign permission sets, turn on Digital Lending and Know Your Customer, and update object permissions.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions.

Assign Digital Lending Permissions:
- Assign Financial Services Cloud Extensions permission sets to the users who set up Digital Lending.
- Enable Digital Lending to grant access to Digital Lending assets and data model.
- Turn on Know Your Customer (KYC) data model to store information collected from a party during a KYC process.
- Customize the Co-Applicant Application by using Apex Class to remove Primary picklist value.
- Download and Implement Digital Lending Sample Data stored in GitHub repository.
- Enable Associated Object Access for Identity Document, Party Identity Verification, etc.
- Note: Usage of certain Digital Lending features impacts event credit consumption.
title: Configuring Digital Lending for Financial Services Cloud
